# MIYAR 2.0 — Intelligent Intake System Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete AI-powered project intake system replacing manual form entry with multimodal AI analysis + per-section AI suggestions.

---

## Phase 2.0-A–D: Intelligent Intake Canvas

| Component | File | What |
|-----------|------|------|
| Schema | [drizzle/schema.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/drizzle/schema.ts) | Extended `project_assets` with `assetType`, `aiExtractionResult`, `aiContributions` |
| Engine | [server/engines/intake/ai-intake-engine.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/intake/ai-intake-engine.ts) | Multimodal Gemini processing (images, PDFs, audio, video, URLs, text) |
| Router | [server/routers/intake.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/routers/intake.ts) | 5 endpoints: upload, record, list, process, link assets |
| UI | [client/src/pages/ProjectNew.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/pages/ProjectNew.tsx) | Drag-drop upload, URL input, voice recording, AI review phase |

## Phase 2.0-E: AI Assist on ProjectForm (This Session)

Added per-section AI Assist buttons to the 7-step ProjectForm wizard.

### Backend
- **[suggestSectionFields()](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/intake/ai-intake-engine.ts#554-719)** in [ai-intake-engine.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/intake/ai-intake-engine.ts) — Maps 6 sections to their fields, calls `invokeLLM` with section-focused prompt, returns `SectionSuggestion[]` with value, confidence, and reasoning per field
- **[suggestSection](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/intake/ai-intake-engine.ts#554-719)** endpoint in [intake.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/routers/intake.ts) — Takes `section` name + `currentFormState`, returns suggestions

### Frontend
- **[AiSectionAssist](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/components/ProjectForm.tsx#609-800)** component (225 lines) in [ProjectForm.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/components/ProjectForm.tsx):
  - ✨ Sparkle button in CardHeader for steps 0–5 (not Review)
  - Per-field Accept ✓ / Dismiss ✕ with confidence badges (HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW)
  - "Accept All" batch action
  - Loading state ("Thinking...") + toast notifications

